Halucigen felt a small door open for him to enter.  Once he was in, 
he had noticed the protections set up.  "Hmmph....I could hack 
through those in a nano Dark one.  But that is not my reason, I 
need off this island now.  If you want me to fight with you, get me 
out of here." the bot spoke through his mind.  To Galvatron it would 
seem as if Halucigen was right there in his mind.
